<body>
    <h1>How to Create a Prolific Account</h1>
    <p>Follow these steps to sign up for a Prolific account as a research participant.</p>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 1: Visit the Prolific Website</h2>
        <p>Go to <a href="https://www.prolific.com/">Prolific's official website</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 2: Click on "Sign Up"</h2>
        <p>On the homepage, click the "Sign Up" button at the top right corner.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 3: Choose "Participant" Account</h2>
        <p>When prompted, select "I want to take part in studies" to proceed.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 4: Enter Your Details</h2>
        <p>Fill in your email, create a password, and enter your basic personal information.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 5: Verify Your Email</h2>
        <p>Check your inbox for a verification email and click the link inside to confirm your account.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 6: Complete Your Profile</h2>
        <p>Log in to your account and complete your demographic profile to qualify for studies.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 7: Start Taking Studies</h2>
        <p>Once your profile is complete, browse available studies and start participating.</p>
    </div>
</body>
